                "html": "Skitterstitches are eight-legged skinstitches crafted to resemble giant spiders. These elite skinstitch variants have different attacks from the standard skinstitch (See <i>Pathfinder #158: Sixty Feet Under</i> page 43), including a deadly poison. Skitterstitches always house spider swarms within their bodies, which scuttle forth when their host is destroyed.\n"
            }
